NK038(nyi)002:1: // dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i sgrubs thabs bzhugs so //
NK038(nyi)002:3: sh+r+ai n+aa tha ka ta la sta na b+ha la la ta pa d+ha tsakra sa d+ha n+aa ma /
NK038(nyi)002:5: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol
NK038(nyi)002:6: pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba
NK038(nyi)002:7: / dpal sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po shin tu rnam par rol pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)002:8: gsang ba gnad kyi rgyud dag las /
NK038(nyi)002:9: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:10: mgon po'i bsgrub pa'i rim pa zhig /
NK038(nyi)002:11: legs par dus la bstan par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:12: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK038(nyi)002:13: byang chub sems ldan bsnyen pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:14: gdeng dang ldan pa'i sngags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:15: bsod nams tshogs ni ci nus bsags //
NK038(nyi)002:16: mchod gtor btang zhing phud btang la //
NK038(nyi)002:17: bden brdar la sogs sngon 'gro bya //
NK038(nyi)002:18: de nas drag po'i las la 'jug /
NK038(nyi)002:19: ra ba bzhi la bsnyen pa tsam //
NK038(nyi)002:20: drag po gza' skar dar pa 'am //
NK038(nyi)002:21: tha chung bzhi la bsad pa brtsam //
NK038(nyi)002:22: dur khrod la sogs rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)002:23: ri brag bzang po'i rtse mo'am //
NK038(nyi)002:24: nags tshal brtsub pa'i sa phyogs kun //
NK038(nyi)002:25: sbrul dug la sogs gcan 'khra yod //
NK038(nyi)002:26: gnas der 'jam dpal mtshan nas brjod //
NK038(nyi)002:27: rdo rje lcam dral gzungs kyang 'don //
NK038(nyi)002:28: gong ma lta bu'i sa dag la //
NK038(nyi)002:30: bdud rtsi khrag gi chag chag gdab //
NK038(nyi)002:31: dur skra'i rgyud chen thig gdab la //
NK038(nyi)002:32: dur khrod mtshon gyi dkyil 'khor bri //
NK038(nyi)002:33: dbus su mu khyud zlum pos bskor //
NK038(nyi)002:34: lcags mkhar lnga dang btsan mkhar bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:35: gru chad bar khyams sgo bzhi ldan //
NK038(nyi)002:36: 'khor yug lcags ri'i phyi rol du //
NK038(nyi)002:37: khrag dang sha chen gshang gci dang //
NK038(nyi)002:38: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)002:39: rnag dang chu ser la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)002:40: 'dam gyi khru ma brgyad kyi bskor //
NK038(nyi)002:41: dbus su yab yum mchog phur dgod //
NK038(nyi)002:42: mkhar bzhi dregs pa bzhi po la //
NK038(nyi)002:43: lcags sam dug shing phur pa dgod //
NK038(nyi)002:44: lho sgor thod pa mtshan ldan du //
NK038(nyi)002:45: dpal bshos khrag dang snying sna tshang //
NK038(nyi)002:46: la phug la du sbyar ba'i sman //
NK038(nyi)002:47: byang du thod pa gtor ma la //
NK038(nyi)002:48: rkang dang klad pa 'bru mar chang //
NK038(nyi)002:49: sbyar ba'i mchod pa yum la bsham //
NK038(nyi)002:50: shar sgo 'bru yi phung po spungs //
NK038(nyi)002:51: nub tu sha sna snying sna dang //
NK038(nyi)002:52: me tog mdzes pa'i tshom bu bri //
NK038(nyi)002:53: dbus su thod pa mtshan ldan gnyis //
NK038(nyi)002:54: steng la bsnyen sgrub sngags bzhi bri //
NK038(nyi)002:56: lug nag snying dang dre bo'i don //
NK038(nyi)002:57: bzang drug chos sman 'bru sna blug /
NK038(nyi)002:58: kha sbyar dar dril rgyu mas bsdams //
NK038(nyi)002:59: h'u gis rgyas gdab khri la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:60: sha khrag nang khrol tsit+ta sogs //
NK038(nyi)002:61: bam gsar rdzas kyi ro ras kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:62: khyams la sogs par mtha' ma bskor //
NK038(nyi)002:63: spos chen mar me chen po dang //
NK038(nyi)002:64: rak+ta'i gsang nan chang gi sbyar //
NK038(nyi)002:65: thod pa'i rnga dang rkang gling dang //
NK038(nyi)002:66: shun gyi rgyal mtshan phyogs bzhir dgram //
NK038(nyi)002:67: zhing gi bla res man+dala dbub //
NK038(nyi)002:68: bdag nyid yi dam lhar gsal te //
NK038(nyi)002:71: bgegs rnams tshar bcad tshul 'dus pas //
NK038(nyi)002:72: rdo rje rwa ba gur gyis bsdams //
NK038(nyi)002:73: me ris brgyan pa'i dbus nyid du //
NK038(nyi)002:74: 'od las gyur pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)002:75: dkon mchog bla ma yi dam lha //
NK038(nyi)002:76: spyan drangs zla ba'i gdan la bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:77: sngon bzhin mchod la sdig pa bshags //
NK038(nyi)002:78: rgyan dang mchod gtor byin rlabs las //
NK038(nyi)002:79: rang gi las rnams rdzogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:80: mgon po'i dkyil 'khor gsum yin te //
NK038(nyi)002:81: bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK038(nyi)002:82: lhar gsal thugs las smug nag b+h+r+aum //
NK038(nyi)002:84: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)002:86: stong gsum shong zhing yangs pa bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:87: mi rta ro rlon nyi gdan la //
NK038(nyi)002:89: sngags 'di brjod pas yab yum bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:90: bur kur ma h+aa kro la kro d+ha h'u //
NK038(nyi)002:91: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri drag mo he //
NK038(nyi)002:92: mgon po tshogs bdag chen po ni //
NK038(nyi)002:93: ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug brjid //
NK038(nyi)002:94: g.yas ser g.yon dmar ljang nag 'jigs //
NK038(nyi)002:95: kham nag dbu skra gyen du bardzesa //
NK038(nyi)002:96: spyan gsum sdang mig skar ltar 'khrug /
NK038(nyi)002:97: shun gos thod pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK038(nyi)002:98: stag shams glang chen thal ba zhag /
NK038(nyi)002:99: gdug pa'i brgyan ldan chas kyi mdzes //
NK038(nyi)002:100: g.yas kyi dang po gsal shing 'phyar //
NK038(nyi)002:101: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK038(nyi)002:103: g.yon gyi dang po thod khrag 'thung //
NK038(nyi)002:104: bar pa rno dbal shun gyi mdung //
NK038(nyi)002:105: tha ma sbrul nag zhags pa bsdoms //
NK038(nyi)002:106: zhabs bzhi gyad kyi dor stabs can //
NK038(nyi)002:107: dbang drag me yi klong du bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:108: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)002:109: 'jigs tshul zhal gcig phyag gnyis rngams //
NK038(nyi)002:110: zhing dang re lde thod sbrul brgyan //
NK038(nyi)002:111: g.yas pa rgyu zhags yab la 'khyud //
NK038(nyi)002:112: g.yon pa thod skyogs rak+ta chang //
NK038(nyi)002:113: rkang dang klad rgyas 'bru mar chang //
NK038(nyi)002:114: rtag par rang gi longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)002:115: mkhar bzhir khro bo rnon po dang //
NK038(nyi)002:116: srin po ma gdon 'jigs pa bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:117: phyi rim gdug pa'i ma tshogs bskyed /
NK038(nyi)002:118: srin mo nye gnas chen po brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:119: ke'u ri tse'u ri pra mo h+aa //
NK038(nyi)002:120: pe ta li dang pu ka si //
NK038(nyi)002:121: kasma ri dang sman sha ri //
NK038(nyi)002:122: tsan+da li la sogs pa kun //
NK038(nyi)002:123: gtum zhing rngam pa'i ma tshogs ma //
NK038(nyi)002:124: shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs su bsgoms //
NK038(nyi)002:125: srin po'i bu mo sham pa brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:126: seng stag wa sbyangs bzhad kyi mgo /
NK038(nyi)002:127: kam ka bya rog 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)002:128: zhing la rngams zhing bstod pa'i tshul //
NK038(nyi)002:129: dur khrod pa yi sgo srung bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:130: brtson mo gdong mo 'gar log ma //
NK038(nyi)002:131: mjug byed las kyi ma mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:132: gsang sgo 'dzin cing bka' sgo bsrungs //
NK038(nyi)002:133: dur khrod bdag mo gru 'debs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:134: skam ma shin tu skam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)002:135: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)002:136: chags pas gdungs pa'i tshul du gnas //
NK038(nyi)002:137: phyi rim slas dang byi mo bran //
NK038(nyi)002:138: ma mo phra men gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)002:139: srin mo sha za khrag phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)002:140: bdud kyi ming 'dzin bla rkun mo //
NK038(nyi)002:141: blon mo dmag dpon sde dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)002:142: ru dpon pho nya mngag par bcas //
NK038(nyi)002:143: ci bgyi bka' nyan dregs pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)002:144: rbod gtong rngams pa'i tshul du bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:145: kun kyang srin mo'i cha lugs ma //
NK038(nyi)002:146: nad kyi bskal pa 'tshum mar gtong //
NK038(nyi)002:147: gdug pa'i mtshon cha lus la 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)002:148: mkhar dang 'obs bar phyi rol na //
NK038(nyi)002:150: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)002:151: sbrul dang sdig pa dom la sogs /
NK038(nyi)002:152: kam ka ru rtse 'ug pa khwa //
NK038(nyi)002:153: bya gcan sha za tshogs rnams lding //
NK038(nyi)002:154: lce spyang stag gzig dom dred 'phar //
NK038(nyi)002:155: dur khrod zhing gi longs spyod la /
NK038(nyi)002:156: lta zhing rgyug cing 'drad pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:157: rgyu ma 'dren cing sha rus za //
NK038(nyi)002:158: de ltar gsal bar gyur pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:159: rang bzhin gnas nas bkug la bstim //
NK038(nyi)002:160: sprul pas bsgral zhing zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:161: phyar du sbyangs nas gnam du ston /
NK038(nyi)002:162: khang pa'i dme sngags bka' 'khor phum //
NK038(nyi)002:163: rang dam bcas bzhin mna' yi bor //
NK038(nyi)002:164: 'khor la bka' sdod dam tshig dbog /
NK038(nyi)002:165: brtag par bya zhing mchod pa rtag /
NK038(nyi)002:166: mnga' gsol phrin las bcol ba dang //
NK038(nyi)002:167: thugs dam bskul zhing bsnyen sngags bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:168: bur kur ma h+aa pad+ma rde chung 'bur tsi 'bur byi ge byi ma na ye /
NK038(nyi)002:169: e ho sha mo kro ta h'u h'u phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)002:170: bdag nyid lhar gsal thugs kar ni //
NK038(nyi)002:171: ye shes sems dpa' nyi dkyil h'u //
NK038(nyi)002:172: mdun du mgon po'i thugs ka ru //
NK038(nyi)002:173: srog bdag 'od zer sna lnga'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)002:174: don la rang gi snying pos bskor //
NK038(nyi)002:176: mgon po'i thugs kar phog pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:177: sngon gyi dam tshig dran gyur nas //
NK038(nyi)002:178: ci bgyi zer zhing las rnams byed //
NK038(nyi)002:179: 'dus pas bdag nyid bka' sdod mngag /
NK038(nyi)002:180: 'bum phrag gcig tu bzlas pa bya //
NK038(nyi)002:181: skabs su mchod bstod longs spyod dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:182: sngon du bsnyen pa'i gdams pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:183: las la drag tu sbyar ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)002:184: nye bsnyen gnad kyi sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:185: dbus kyi phur pa'am rten dag la //
NK038(nyi)002:186: dkar nag mthing kha'i gzungs thag gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:187: mthing nag dar chen nang du ni //
NK038(nyi)002:188: dang po yungs dkar rgyal po blug /
NK038(nyi)002:189: bar du khrag sna tshang ma dang //
NK038(nyi)002:190: tsan dan dmar po sbyar la blug /
NK038(nyi)002:191: tha ma tsan dan dkar po dang //
NK038(nyi)002:192: bzang drug bdud rtsi sbyar la blug /
NK038(nyi)002:193: de steng nyi dkyil pad+ma la //
NK038(nyi)002:194: zla ba'i kha la yig 'bru gsum //
NK038(nyi)002:195: h+r+aihdakara rwa dmar mthing nag h'u //
NK038(nyi)002:196: sngags 'dir rang dbang brgya brgya bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:197: badz+ra kro ta r+aa dza ya //
NK038(nyi)002:201: g+h+rih+na g+h+rih+na ma ke na h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:202: yungs kar dam tshig khro bo ni //
NK038(nyi)002:204: h+r+aihbadz+ra yak+sha ta g+h+rih+na ra ka ma h+aa k+aa ru h'u phatahranga gi 'od kyi bde gshegs kyi /
NK038(nyi)002:205: thugs rje 'khor ba'i chags pa bsdus //
NK038(nyi)002:206: mi brjed gzungs kyi dam rdzas skyil //
NK038(nyi)002:207: badz+ra tsit+ta sa ma ya amri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK038(nyi)002:208: bde gshegs zag med bdud rtsi dbab //
NK038(nyi)002:209: zug rngu 'byin pa' nang du bskyil //
NK038(nyi)002:210: bskul dang 'brel dang zug rngu sel //
NK038(nyi)002:211: rim pa'i tshul du gdags par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:212: bdag nyid yi dam lhar gsal ba'i //
NK038(nyi)002:213: thugs kar rdo rje srin po bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:214: nye bsnyen gnad kyi sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:215: b+hu ru ku ru ma a pra na su tsi ki phyi ma na se kha //
NK038(nyi)002:216: shwa mo kro d+ha h'u h'u phata phata //
NK038(nyi)002:217: sngags kyi 'od zer rno myur drag /
NK038(nyi)002:218: dam tshig khro bo nye tshe 'phro //
NK038(nyi)002:219: mgon po dbang med gnas nas 'gugs //
NK038(nyi)002:220: rang nyid srog la drod langs nas //
NK038(nyi)002:221: lus ngag yid gsum tsha zhing gdung //
NK038(nyi)002:222: 'bum phrag gcig tu rdzogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:226: sa la mi thogs chur mi 'bying //
NK038(nyi)002:227: legs ldan mdun na ci bya zer //
NK038(nyi)002:228: rab kyi rtags su shes par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:229: rten la me 'bar tsheg pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:230: sman phud khol zhing rak+ta lud //
NK038(nyi)002:231: rten gyi zhal bzhad nyams byung srid //
NK038(nyi)002:232: sman gyi thum bu kha phye la //
NK038(nyi)002:233: bdud rtsi nang du btab nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:234: rten nam ting 'dzin gzugs la gtor //
NK038(nyi)002:235: sku yi tsha ba gzhil bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:236: sku gsung rang bzhin mnal ma ni //
NK038(nyi)002:237: bdag la bka' nod las rnams byed //
NK038(nyi)002:238: dngos grub bdag dbang bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:239: sgrub pa'i rim pa bag tsam sbyar //
NK038(nyi)002:240: rak+ta chang sbyar rten la gtor //
NK038(nyi)002:241: thugs rjes chags pa bskyed bya zhing //
NK038(nyi)002:242: sngon du bsnyen pa shas tsam btang //
NK038(nyi)002:243: yungs kar rgyal po brab byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:244: nye bsnyen gnad nas stong phrag dgug /
NK038(nyi)002:245: bsgrub pa'i gsang sngags 'di dag bzlas /
NK038(nyi)002:246: b+hu ru gu ru i byi u d+ma kro ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:247: 'od zer lcags kyu dbang gi mdog /
NK038(nyi)002:248: 'phros te rang bzhin mgon po la //
NK038(nyi)002:249: dam tshig bskul zhing mchod pa byas //
NK038(nyi)002:250: dngos grub chags pa'i mdog lta bu //
NK038(nyi)002:251: bsdu zhing rang la bstim pa bya //
NK038(nyi)002:252: phyed shas tsam gyis gnad la phebs //
NK038(nyi)002:253: mthun mjug sman gyi tsha ba gzhil //
NK038(nyi)002:255: sgrub khang g.yo zhing 'gyur la tsheg /
NK038(nyi)002:256: yams dang nad kyi bu yug thul //
NK038(nyi)002:258: re dam chol dang cig rlangs 'byung //
NK038(nyi)002:259: tha ma'i rmi lam ston par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:260: dgra bcom tshogs su 'ong ba dang //
NK038(nyi)002:261: slob dpon ban d+he mon nag dang /
NK038(nyi)002:262: rlung nag tshub ma chu nag 'brug /
NK038(nyi)002:263: g.yag khyu'i tshogs dang bya nag lding //
NK038(nyi)002:265: skar mda' mang po lhung pa 'byung //
NK038(nyi)002:266: bsnyen dang nye ba'i rtags su shes //
NK038(nyi)002:267: rten gyi thod pa kha phye la //
NK038(nyi)002:268: myos pa'i rdzas dang bu ram dang //
NK038(nyi)002:269: bdud rtsi 'o skam zhal zas bsham /
NK038(nyi)002:270: de bzhin mchod pa kun kyang btang //
NK038(nyi)002:271: dmar ljang dar gyi ling+ga bri //
NK038(nyi)002:272: rdzas rnams bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs //
NK038(nyi)002:273: nang du srog gsum yi ge bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:274: mgon po'i gzhung bsrang snying po bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:276: sarba sid+d+hi pha la h'u +aah chags phyir rak+ta'i thum pos mchod //
NK038(nyi)002:278: brgyad kyi dngos grub mthu byin ba sdus //
NK038(nyi)002:279: 'bum phrag rdzogs nas srog gsum zhu //
NK038(nyi)002:280: dngos grub rdzas la bdag nyid rol //
NK038(nyi)002:281: tshe dang chos dang longs spyod sdus //
NK038(nyi)002:282: drag po mthu yi dngos grub blang //
NK038(nyi)002:283: dam can gtor ma tshogs kyis mchod //
NK038(nyi)002:284: sman gyi mchod pas stobs ldan 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:285: bsnyen pa'i rdul mtshon zhal phyes la //
NK038(nyi)002:286: drag po las la sbyar bar bya //
NK038(nyi)002:287: bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK038(nyi)002:290: rak+ta khrag gi dmar por byug /
NK038(nyi)002:291: dbus nas mnyam pa'i shing bzhag la //
NK038(nyi)002:292: mda' gang zlum pos bskor nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:293: mtho gang tshad du gyen du brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)002:294: dbus nas khru gang gru ga sum pa //
NK038(nyi)002:295: nang rim gsum ldan thur du bru //
NK038(nyi)002:296: kha la thod pa'i phreng ba btang //
NK038(nyi)002:297: dug shing rtsang dmar nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:298: mtshon cha rdo rje 'khor lo dang //
NK038(nyi)002:299: ral gri dbyug pa rgya gram lngas //
NK038(nyi)002:300: 'og ma dag la bskor bar bya //
NK038(nyi)002:301: dmigs pa dgra yi rdzas drug dang //
NK038(nyi)002:302: bag phye sa sbyin bsres pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)002:303: bcu gnyis sor tshad ming rus snag /
NK038(nyi)002:304: kan d+ha'i shing la ming rus bri //
NK038(nyi)002:305: dred mo'i skra thag sngo dmar gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:306: bcings nas mgo brnyan grtsang la gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:307: dur khrod g.yam sa khru gang la //
NK038(nyi)002:308: dbus nas mtho gang gru gsum bru //
NK038(nyi)002:309: 'brub steng bzhag la thod mkhar bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:310: rgya ni de dang mthun pa la //
NK038(nyi)002:311: dpangs su sor bzhi bstod la brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)002:312: rang ngos thel la sgo bstan pa //
NK038(nyi)002:313: logs bzhir phrin las glo skar bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:314: phyogs bzhir mkhar bzhi phyed shes bya //
NK038(nyi)002:315: dur khrod mtshon gyi ri mo yis //
NK038(nyi)002:316: stag dang mi rta bya ya mgo /
NK038(nyi)002:317: srin po'i thod pas ba gam bya //
NK038(nyi)002:318: nang du rten gyi phur pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)002:319: yang na bka' rten brag nag dred //
NK038(nyi)002:320: dur khrod sa srin gzugs byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:321: mtshon gyi bsgyur la phyag mtshan gtad //
NK038(nyi)002:322: mkhar rnams kun gyi rgyud dag ni //
NK038(nyi)002:323: bka' rten chos khri dur khrod dang /
NK038(nyi)002:324: gnod sbyin yul dang rgyal po'i khab //
NK038(nyi)002:325: phyug po'i bang mdzod rin chen rtse //
NK038(nyi)002:326: sa sna bdun la klu chus bru //
NK038(nyi)002:327: phyogs bzhir ru mtshon nag po bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:328: phyogs bzhir bdud bya nag po lding //
NK038(nyi)002:329: snyug ma tshigs lnga'i mda' gcig la //
NK038(nyi)002:330: dri med drag po bcug nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:331: bya rgod srin bya 'ug pa khwa //
NK038(nyi)002:332: lnga sgron mda' la dar nag gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:333: g.yu mig nam mkha' nag po la //
NK038(nyi)002:334: rgod kyi sgro gzugs dar gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)002:335: dbus kyi mkhar stengs bzhag par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:336: g.yas g.yon yab yum gtor ma bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:337: snying gsum dar dril lus la bcangs //
NK038(nyi)002:338: rten gyi sku gzugs mda' la gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:339: gying gi mkhar gyi stengs logs su //
NK038(nyi)002:340: lcags phur bcu gnyis dar gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)002:341: ral gri mtho gang gri lcags byug /
NK038(nyi)002:342: pho snying sna tshogs gtor ma bcas //
NK038(nyi)002:343: lho phyogs gnod sbyin mkhar stengs su //
NK038(nyi)002:344: bse mdung khru gang dar gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)002:345: zor mda' mor thod g.yas g.yon dgod //
NK038(nyi)002:346: ru skyogs mdzes pa'i nang nyid du //
NK038(nyi)002:347: ra dmar bya dmar gri bo'i don //
NK038(nyi)002:348: mar khu sbrang rtsi 'o ma khrag /
NK038(nyi)002:349: sbyar ba'i gtor ma bdud rtsir bcas //
NK038(nyi)002:350: nub phyogs srin po'i mkhar stengs su //
NK038(nyi)002:351: sbrul sha dug dang bag phye sbyar //
NK038(nyi)002:352: sbrul mgo gsum ldan 'khyil ba bca' //
NK038(nyi)002:353: kan d+ha'i dgra gzugs stengs su bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:354: g.yas su sha rul khrag rul dang //
NK038(nyi)002:355: snying gi tshogs kyis thod pa dgang //
NK038(nyi)002:356: g.yon du ba dmar thod pa la //
NK038(nyi)002:357: klu sman btab la mkhar gzhong bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:358: byang du za byed mkhar stengs su //
NK038(nyi)002:359: tshon drug nam mkha' dar nag brgyan //
NK038(nyi)002:360: gtor ma tshil chen sprin kheb can //
NK038(nyi)002:361: lid+ga rma bya'i gdugs dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)002:362: byan lag mchongs kyi ri bo la //
NK038(nyi)002:363: dug shing yal ga dur khrod kyi //
NK038(nyi)002:364: sha rus bcas pa thod phor gram //
NK038(nyi)002:365: kang ka thang dmar mtsho 'gram la //
NK038(nyi)002:366: dpal gtor rak+ta bdud rtsi dang //
NK038(nyi)002:367: spos chen snum chen la sogs dgram //
NK038(nyi)002:368: gru bzhi ha sta'i rgyal mtshan gzugs //
NK038(nyi)002:369: zhing gi bla re man+dala dbub //
NK038(nyi)002:370: mon thod nang du dug sna dang //
NK038(nyi)002:371: khrag sna gsum mtshon dbal brdar la //
NK038(nyi)002:372: chang gi sbyar la byang du dgod //
NK038(nyi)002:373: de bzhin rigs ngan thod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)002:374: yungs dkar yungs nag skyee tshe dang //
NK038(nyi)002:375: tsha ba sna tshogs lho ru dgod //
NK038(nyi)002:376: de ltar bca' bzhi rdzogs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:377: phyogs bzhi sngon bzhin gsol ba gdab //
NK038(nyi)002:378: dpal gyi las gsum rdzogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:379: de yang 'bru brgyad rbad gsad bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)002:380: bdag nyid lha yi nga rgyal las //
NK038(nyi)002:381: thugs las 'od zer rim pa ru //
NK038(nyi)002:382: bam las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:383: de ltar lam las drag shul ri //
NK038(nyi)002:384: ta na 'ba' ti dur khrod gnas //
NK038(nyi)002:385: b+h+aum las thod pa'i mkhar lnga bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:386: dbus su dmigs pa'i dgra stengs su //
NK038(nyi)002:387: don las rtsa ba'i sngags brjod pas //
NK038(nyi)002:388: legs ldan yab yum sngon bzhin bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:389: yang na zhal gcig phyag gnyis ljang //
NK038(nyi)002:390: gsal shing phyar nas shun gyi mdung //
NK038(nyi)002:391: dur khrod chas rnams rdzogs par bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:392: mdun du las grub bka' sdod ni //
NK038(nyi)002:393: nag po gri gug thod pa 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)002:394: phyogs bzhir gtso bo'i thugs ka nas //
NK038(nyi)002:395: h'u dang ya dza ma bzhi spros //
NK038(nyi)002:396: sngags brjod 'khor dang bcas pa bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:397: shar du khro bo ging ka ra //
NK038(nyi)002:398: mthing ga mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)002:399: snying khrag 'thung zhing dmigs pa gnon //
NK038(nyi)002:400: phyi na gri thogs bcu gnyis gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:401: kun kyang khro tshul 'jigs pa'i tshul //
NK038(nyi)002:402: dur khrod rgyan ldan gar stobs bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)002:403: ral gri 'dar zhing glo snying za //
NK038(nyi)002:405: lho ru ya las gnod sbyin gtso //
NK038(nyi)002:406: dmar nag zhing chen ral pa khrag /
NK038(nyi)002:407: gser gyi ral gri mdung dmar 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)002:408: yum ni bya thag nad rkyal 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)002:409: skyes bu bzhi dang se mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:410: mi dmar bshan pa bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK038(nyi)002:411: 'jig rten skyes pa'i cha lugs rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:412: nub tu ra las ra hu la //
NK038(nyi)002:413: dud kha mgo dgu ro smad sbrul //
NK038(nyi)002:414: mgo lus kun gsal ral pa khrag /
NK038(nyi)002:415: gri gug thod pa bsnams pa'o //
NK038(nyi)002:416: srin po bcu dang srin mo bcu //
NK038(nyi)002:417: mtshon cha rno dbal longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)002:418: byang du ma las za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)002:419: mthing nag ral pa dug rlangs can //
NK038(nyi)002:420: shun gos re lde rgyu 'phreng zhags //
NK038(nyi)002:421: seng sprul nyi zla chas kun rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:422: g.yas pa khram shing nad rkyal g.yon //
NK038(nyi)002:423: dred nag zhon nas me dpung dbus //
NK038(nyi)002:424: rlung nag 'tshub ma'i dkyil na bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)002:426: gzhan yang ma mo'i 'khor gyi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)002:428: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan drangs la //
NK038(nyi)002:429: dur khrod gnas su bstan par stim //
NK038(nyi)002:431: phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK038(nyi)002:432: dam tshig rten pa dag dang sbyar //
NK038(nyi)002:433: mchod pa'i rim pa tshul bzhin dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:434: de ltar bla rdo bcang zhing bzung //
NK038(nyi)002:435: pha wang long bu'i rdo ba la //
NK038(nyi)002:436: tsa ra rog po'i snying khrag gi /
NK038(nyi)002:437: h'u dang hri ya dza ma bri //
NK038(nyi)002:438: yungs kar nang du bcug la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:439: h'u gi dam tshig khro bo la //
NK038(nyi)002:440: gzhi ni 'khor lo bla rdo srog /
NK038(nyi)002:441: lcags thig ngos la rdo nag dug /
NK038(nyi)002:442: dun bri yab kyi bla rdo srog /
NK038(nyi)002:444: ma bris yum gyi bla rdo yin //
NK038(nyi)002:445: gnyis ka chags pa'i snod du gzhug /
NK038(nyi)002:446: sman la yi dam snying po'am //
NK038(nyi)002:447: dpa' bo 'bru lnga bris la gzhug /
NK038(nyi)002:448: gzungs thag gdags la changs bar bzung //
NK038(nyi)002:449: thun mtshams lcags phur dbal la gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:450: yungs dkar drag po khro bo yis //
NK038(nyi)002:451: dbang bskur drag tu bkrad la bskul //
NK038(nyi)002:452: bsnyen dang nye bsnyen shas tsam btang //
NK038(nyi)002:453: sgrub sngags drag po bcu bzhi pas //
NK038(nyi)002:454: dbang med srog yig tshang bar bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:455: myur tu dgug cing rten la bstim //
NK038(nyi)002:456: skabs su sman gyi tsha ba gzhil //
NK038(nyi)002:457: sha khrag gtor ma phud kyis mchod //
NK038(nyi)002:458: skabs skabs rten la yungs kar brab //
NK038(nyi)002:459: bsgrub sngags nyid dang sprul pa bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:460: 'bar ba'i tshig gis dmigs pa'i mir //
NK038(nyi)002:461: srog la b+h+yo b+h+yo sbyar cing bskul //
NK038(nyi)002:462: bcu gnyis mtha' la rbad sngags gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:463: b+hu ru ku ru i byi u tsash+ma kro ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:464: kro ta yak+sha rak+sha tsit+ta sa ma ya b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:465: b+hur ma ha ka la r+n+ri thums lam thum ril rbad su r+n+ri dza /
NK038(nyi)002:468: r+n+ri thum ril rbad snying kha rag r+n+ri dza b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:469: yungs kar khro bo'i mthun gyis brab //
NK038(nyi)002:470: dam tshig khro bo'i dbang po bskul //
NK038(nyi)002:471: sde bzhi sprul pa 'khor bcas kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:472: dmigs pa'i dgra bo'i yul khams bkang //
NK038(nyi)002:473: bla dang shes pa dgug cing stim //
NK038(nyi)002:474: dpal mgon po nag po 'khor bcas rbad //
NK038(nyi)002:476: thun mtshams gu gul me dud btang //
NK038(nyi)002:477: gang yin lha la thun gyis brab //
NK038(nyi)002:478: rak+ta khrag sbyar sku la gtor //
NK038(nyi)002:479: thugs rje rgyun dang ldan par bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:481: kun kyang bye ru'i mdog ltar bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:482: chags pas g.yel med phrin las dran //
NK038(nyi)002:483: go mtshon cha la rdung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)002:485: las la tshud pa'i mtshan ma yin //
NK038(nyi)002:487: drag po las la sbyor ba la //
NK038(nyi)002:488: phur pa'i dgongs pa gong bzhin sbyar //
NK038(nyi)002:489: ci nas las myur rang la shis //
NK038(nyi)002:490: nus pa mi chor g.yel ba med //
NK038(nyi)002:491: nyin mo rbad cing dmigs pas dgug /
NK038(nyi)002:492: de nas bsad pa'i sngags 'di sbrel //
NK038(nyi)002:493: ma h+aa ka la r+n+ri dzah snying la thum ril
NK038(nyi)002:494: rus pa la rbad su rbad su r+n+ri sha tsit+ta
NK038(nyi)002:497: snying la r+n+ri dza dzah srog la tsa bam snying la ya ya /
NK038(nyi)002:498: hab hab r+n+ri ma ra ya phatah nyi ma dmar thag chad pa la /
NK038(nyi)002:499: pho yi reg chod sngags 'di gdags //
NK038(nyi)002:500: sh+ri he g+ho dza shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:501: mu ro tsit+ta ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:502: re ge sho ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:503: ya me te sha ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:504: ra hu ra na ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:505: tsi t+ta ri ma ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:506: sha na dur khrod khrmo badz+ra sha ti tshe srog ma ra ya rbad rbad /
NK038(nyi)002:507: skam thun thun khrag nang nas brab //
NK038(nyi)002:508: mchog phur las kyi mgon por bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:509: snying la gdab cing dwangs snyigs 'byed //
NK038(nyi)002:510: gsang ba'i rnga brdung drag tu bskul //
NK038(nyi)002:511: dregs pa pho rnams srog la rngub //
NK038(nyi)002:512: bka' sdod las kyi bshan pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:513: gri gug khog gshags snying phyungs nas //
NK038(nyi)002:514: gtso bo'i zhal du btab par bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:515: gnod sbyin tshogs dang mche gshogs gis //
NK038(nyi)002:516: sha khrag za zhing rgyu ma 'dren //
NK038(nyi)002:517: pho gshed gnad kyi reg chod kyi //
NK038(nyi)002:518: dmigs pa rlag pa'i 'phrin las yin //
NK038(nyi)002:519: mtshan mo bsgrub sngags gnyis po la //
NK038(nyi)002:520: bsad sngags sbrel la drag tu bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:521: tho rangs lha 'dre rgyu dus nas //
NK038(nyi)002:522: mo yi reg chod sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:523: ma h+aa k+aa li ma b+h+yo ru lu ru lu sa ma ya b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:524: trag rak+sha kha mun tra b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:525: ru lu ru lu ma ra ya thun b+h+yo traka mo raka /
NK038(nyi)002:526: snying khrag ma ra ya thun ya //
NK038(nyi)002:527: drag mo rag mo che ge mo la thun ya //
NK038(nyi)002:528: dug khrag gsher thun na 'ug dbab //
NK038(nyi)002:529: ma mo srin mo gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)002:530: bdud mo'i tshogs kyi dmag tshogs kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:531: dmigs pa'i lus la nad mtshon gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:533: sngo dmar dug gi rtsa rnams khengs //
NK038(nyi)002:534: snying la 'dus la dwangs snyigs phye //
NK038(nyi)002:535: dang ma chos nyid bde bar thim //
NK038(nyi)002:536: phung po sha khrag ma tshogs rol //
NK038(nyi)002:537: zhag grangs dgu yi ting 'dzin ltar //
NK038(nyi)002:538: thun rdzogs dngos dang 'brel ba'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)002:539: byang shar lcags mkhar sgo med du //
NK038(nyi)002:540: dug shing 'dus pa'i me la bsreg /
NK038(nyi)002:541: pho sngags mo sngags dril la brab //
NK038(nyi)002:542: gser skyems lha 'dre kun la btang //
NK038(nyi)002:543: zor lam phye la bse mda' la //
NK038(nyi)002:544: nang du drag po'i skam thun blug /
NK038(nyi)002:545: thun khrag blug la dug shing mer //
NK038(nyi)002:546: rno dbal dmar nag tshil chen bdug /
NK038(nyi)002:547: drag po'i me sbar dgra la brdeg /
NK038(nyi)002:548: zor gyi rgyal po mched bzhi la //
NK038(nyi)002:549: rgyud las byung ba bzhin du bskul //
NK038(nyi)002:550: bsnyen bsgrub bsad thun kun dril la //
NK038(nyi)002:552: ri li li snyi li li //
NK038(nyi)002:554: srog rtsa ma ra ya rbad //
NK038(nyi)002:555: tsi ta'i dkyil du n+ri dza thun //
NK038(nyi)002:556: khrag gi ser chen phob phob //
NK038(nyi)002:557: mi stegs log lta'i thod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)002:558: thun khrag blug la ngar blangs stim //
NK038(nyi)002:559: dur skra'i mgul rdog khrag mda' 'phang //
NK038(nyi)002:561: lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)002:562: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)002:563: dur khrod bdag po sgrol ba'i ging //
NK038(nyi)002:564: khyad par 'phags pa'i bla ma la //
NK038(nyi)002:565: dang ba'i sems kyi mos btud nas //
NK038(nyi)002:566: mthu chen 'jigs pa'i skyabs tshol na //
NK038(nyi)002:567: dpal gyi spyan sngar dam bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)002:568: chos kyi srung ma dam la 'du //
NK038(nyi)002:569: sngags kyi ma sring las la chos //
NK038(nyi)002:571: mgon po nag po dmag sna drongs //
NK038(nyi)002:573: dgra bo'i lnga phung gshoms pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:574: mu stegs ka la'i thod pa la //
NK038(nyi)002:575: zor gyi gzhu mchog lam se lam //
NK038(nyi)002:576: sngags kyi rgyud sgra breng nge breng //
NK038(nyi)002:577: rak+ta chags pa'i snyug ma la //
NK038(nyi)002:578: gsod byed 'ug pa'i sgro yis skyon //
NK038(nyi)002:579: tsha dbal thun gyi rus kyis dkris //
NK038(nyi)002:580: yungs kar mthun gyi made'u gsal //
NK038(nyi)002:582: dgra bo'i snying la dug mda' ya //
NK038(nyi)002:583: rnam shes rten la dug mda' ya //
NK038(nyi)002:584: ma h+aa ka la che ge mo srog phrig phrig
NK038(nyi)002:585: chum chum hur hur rag mo snying rtsa la breng
NK038(nyi)002:586: breng / dam dam ma ma trag mo traka mo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:587: rgyud la me 'bar chas gos gdab //
NK038(nyi)002:588: srid pa'i lha srin dam bdar sbran //
NK038(nyi)002:589: de ltar drag po'i las rdzogs nas //
NK038(nyi)002:590: bsad pa'i rtags rnams rdzogs par 'byung //
NK038(nyi)002:591: khra yi byi'u ded pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:594: sha la longs spyod gos la rol //
NK038(nyi)002:595: brag chen rtsad nas bton pa ni //
NK038(nyi)002:596: gdung rgyud rtsad nas chad par nges //
NK038(nyi)002:597: sdong po brtsad nas ngo bo 'chi //
NK038(nyi)002:598: zha lag brtsad nas 'gab la ngan //
NK038(nyi)002:599: dngos po bsad nas snying phyung zos //
NK038(nyi)002:600: the tshom med pa'i las yin no //
NK038(nyi)002:601: rgyan phrogs gos shus rogs la ngan //
NK038(nyi)002:602: gzhan yang sgrub pa'i dus dag tu //
NK038(nyi)002:603: mun sprang slong dang longs spyod 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)002:605: gzhan yang nyes legs dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)002:606: sa sna bdun gyi 'dag sa la //
NK038(nyi)002:607: tshad dang ldan pa'i mkhar byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:608: nang du legs ldan gzugs brnyan bstan //
NK038(nyi)002:609: steng du las kyi bya khyung bzhag /
NK038(nyi)002:610: dur khrod ro ras khru gang la //
NK038(nyi)002:611: dmigs pa'i dri ma ha zhig dang //
NK038(nyi)002:612: go ro tsa na sbyar la byug /
NK038(nyi)002:613: sbrul nag 'a khril ba'i dug bar du //
NK038(nyi)002:614: phrag dog sbal pa'i lto ba ru //
NK038(nyi)002:615: rdo srol dug khrag sbyar byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:616: kam ka'i sgro rtsas snyug gu bya //
NK038(nyi)002:617: mu khyud rim pa bzhis bskor te //
NK038(nyi)002:618: ba dmar khrag dang rtsi sman gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:619: dbus su dmigs pa'i li d+ga bri //
NK038(nyi)002:620: g.yas su gnyan mo g.yon du klu //
NK038(nyi)002:621: lus la ming rus rdzogs par bri //
NK038(nyi)002:622: rgyab tu sa bdag 'doms su bzod //
NK038(nyi)002:623: 'byung po'i dug bzhi dmigs pa bzungs //
NK038(nyi)002:624: de yi phyi rim sngags 'di dag /
NK038(nyi)002:625: yig mgo nang du bstan la bri //
NK038(nyi)002:629: e na ga kro ti shwo ri /
NK038(nyi)002:633: hu ya hu ya klu mo'i tshogs /
NK038(nyi)002:635: na ga zhen na ga zhen /
NK038(nyi)002:636: su mo zhen su mo zhen /
NK038(nyi)002:637: pa khrag zhen pa khrag zhe na //
NK038(nyi)002:638: dbugs la thum thum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)002:639: klu srin btud de dbang med 'khril //
NK038(nyi)002:640: de mthar thun khrag sngags 'di dang //
NK038(nyi)002:641: ming byang spel la bri bar bya //
NK038(nyi)002:642: na ga du na ga du /
NK038(nyi)002:645: nag po 'am tsi tsi rgyas trag thur snying la thur /
NK038(nyi)002:647: shan shan che ge mo'i srog la shan /
NK038(nyi)002:650: na ga gur ling snying la 'dus 'dus /
NK038(nyi)002:652: sa ma ya dam dza dzah na ga rak+sha /
NK038(nyi)002:655: bsnyen sgrub bsad mthun nang bstan bri //
NK038(nyi)002:656: dbang phyug legs ldan nag po ni //
NK038(nyi)002:657: 'chi bdag klu yi ded dpon yin //
NK038(nyi)002:658: 'khor lo dril na btsan mdze'i r+aa //
NK038(nyi)002:659: ku ku ka la su pu ra //
NK038(nyi)002:660: tsi ti dz+wa la thod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)002:661: rgya mtshor khro bcu'i rgyas btab nas //
NK038(nyi)002:662: mun pa nag po'i gling du dril //
NK038(nyi)002:663: dkar nag sbrul gyi thag pas bsdams //
NK038(nyi)002:664: rang nyid mgon po nag por bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:665: nag gsum gla tsi khrag dang dug /
NK038(nyi)002:666: dri spos sbyar la lus la byug /
NK038(nyi)002:667: lha srin kun la gser skyems btang //
NK038(nyi)002:668: brten bdag de la rtsi sman sbyin //
NK038(nyi)002:669: nag po rdol ba'i srang na yar //
NK038(nyi)002:670: mda' gang bcal bar dong brus la //
NK038(nyi)002:671: phyogs bzhir mchog gi phur pa bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:672: gshin rje gshed dang rta mgrin dang //
NK038(nyi)002:673: gsang bdag nyid dang sprul pa bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:674: thod pa dong du bcug nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:675: snying po sde gnyis brgya brgya bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:676: mang na rang la klu srin 'du //
NK038(nyi)002:677: de'i stong khams klu rnams kun //
NK038(nyi)002:678: mo rnams chags pa'i tshul gyis 'khril //
NK038(nyi)002:679: pho rnams rngam pa'i zas su za //
NK038(nyi)002:680: khro bo 'khor dang khyung gi mnan //
NK038(nyi)002:681: mgon po'i sngags rnams dril la bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:682: dpal mgon po nag po'i zhabs 'og nas //
NK038(nyi)002:683: 'jig rten klu rnams las byed bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:684: dur g.yam rgya gram steng nas dgab //
NK038(nyi)002:685: nyi shu rtsa gcig phyir bskyed la //
NK038(nyi)002:686: tho gzugs drag po'i dal la bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:687: bskor ba phyi nang 'og tu bya //
NK038(nyi)002:688: dug gi sgro bar bstan pa drud //
NK038(nyi)002:689: dug khrag gtibs la rang rjes dgab //
NK038(nyi)002:690: dgra yi mkhar la chu la rdeg /
NK038(nyi)002:691: slar log bkra shis tshogs mchod bya //
NK038(nyi)002:692: des ni las la the tshom med //
NK038(nyi)002:693: nag po ldog pa'i mtshan ma ni //
NK038(nyi)002:694: mun pa gos dang mdze can rgol //
NK038(nyi)002:695: g.yag rgod rdung zhing gcan zan rmugs //
NK038(nyi)002:696: chu nag gyen la ldog par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:697: cis kyang las 'gyangs log gyur na //
NK038(nyi)002:698: kan d+ha'i shing la mgon po'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)002:699: mtho gang tshad la skye mched rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:700: phyi rol ru lu bzlog pa bri //
NK038(nyi)002:701: lag pa g.yas g.yon bsnyen sngags gnyis //
NK038(nyi)002:702: rkang par sprul pa bsod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)002:703: thun sngags kho rang lus la bri //
NK038(nyi)002:704: de la dgug cing stim byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:705: dgra yi gzugs dang slas byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:706: zhag gsum dpal gtor 'og tu gzir //
NK038(nyi)002:707: bsnyen bsgrub sngags la mas bzlog rdeg /
NK038(nyi)002:708: drag shul 'byung ba'i nyin zhag la //
NK038(nyi)002:709: ral gri 'phyar zhing gnyen po sdigs //
NK038(nyi)002:710: dug shing gdug pa'i me la bsreg /
NK038(nyi)002:711: bka' brten sa la thal ba sbyar //
NK038(nyi)002:712: gzugs byang khong par ming rus gzugs //
NK038(nyi)002:713: mgon po bskyed la bdud rtsi gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:714: mchod pa phul la las gnyer gtad //
NK038(nyi)002:715: dud khrod dbus su dong brus la //
NK038(nyi)002:716: mgon po'i gzugs gzhug dur g.yam dgab //
NK038(nyi)002:717: mchod rten nag po mtho gang la //
NK038(nyi)002:718: zur gsum gu gul nag pos bdug /
NK038(nyi)002:719: steng bzhag bsnyen po pho brang bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:720: lha nyid gnad la dbab pa ste //
NK038(nyi)002:721: ya bag sha ra rab tu gsang //
NK038(nyi)002:722: mngon rol gsang ba'i rgyud dag las //
NK038(nyi)002:723: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:724: dpal mgon sgrub thabs 'di bgyis pas //
NK038(nyi)002:725: sngags pa'i sku dgra sgrol gyur te //
NK038(nyi)002:726: bstan pa yun du gnas par shog /
NK038(nyi)002:727: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol
NK038(nyi)002:728: pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i sgrub thabs rgya gar gyi
NK038(nyi)002:729: mkhas pa dpal rdo rje 'chang gi zhal mthong ba'i
NK038(nyi)002:730: rdo rje h'u mdzad kyi mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK038(nyi)002:731: grub thob bram ze dpal ba'i rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:732: bal po b+ha su d+ha ra la gdams //
NK038(nyi)002:733: des sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la gdams //
NK038(nyi)002:735: g.yas ru smug kyi rdo rje sgrom bu ru gtad pa'i rgya'o //
NK038(nyi)002:737: rgya rgya rgya 'bar ba khro bo phyag rgya dngos grub kyi bsgrub thabs bzhugs so //
NK038(nyi)002:739: kro ta dz+wa la sid+ha mu tra man+da la sa ha na ma /
NK038(nyi)002:741: 'bar ba khro bo phyag rgya dngos grub kyi dkyil
NK038(nyi)002:742: 'khor bsgrub pa'i thabs zhes bya ba bcom ldan 'das
NK038(nyi)002:743: badz+ra he ru ka phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)002:744: mngon rol rgyud kyi rgyal po la //
NK038(nyi)002:745: sems can ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:747: legs par bsdus la bstan par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:748: 'das pa'i dus na mngon byung ba'i //
NK038(nyi)002:749: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:750: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK038(nyi)002:751: 'gro ba'i don du sngon byung ba //
NK038(nyi)002:752: de tshe sems can thams cad kun //
NK038(nyi)002:753: stong nyid ther zug 'gog pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:754: khro gtum log lta rkam zhing 'jungs //
NK038(nyi)002:755: le lo gti mug chags sogs te //
NK038(nyi)002:756: de dag gdul bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:758: rjes su 'jug pa'i bsgrub bya na //
NK038(nyi)002:759: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK038(nyi)002:760: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK038(nyi)002:761: gsang sngags 'phrin bsgrub byed pa de //
NK038(nyi)002:763: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK038(nyi)002:764: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK038(nyi)002:765: khong na gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK038(nyi)002:766: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK038(nyi)002:767: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:768: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:769: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK038(nyi)002:770: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK038(nyi)002:771: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK038(nyi)002:772: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK038(nyi)002:773: gzhan du nam yang sbyin mi bya //
NK038(nyi)002:774: rmongs la 'chal bas gal te byin //
NK038(nyi)002:775: dus min sar ni srog zad nas //
NK038(nyi)002:776: srog dang sbrebs la yun ring gnas //
NK038(nyi)002:777: lha bsgrub dkyil 'khor bzhi yin te //
NK038(nyi)002:778: ji bzhin nyid dang phyag rgya dang //
NK038(nyi)002:779: byang chub sems dang bsod nams tshogs //
NK038(nyi)002:780: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK038(nyi)002:781: dngos po bzhi la gnas bcas kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:782: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)002:783: de ni rnal 'byor dam pa'i lam //
NK038(nyi)002:785: gsang sngags ngo bo de nyid yin //
NK038(nyi)002:786: rdo rje sems pa'i rang bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)002:787: yon tan mtshan grangs du ma'i don //
NK038(nyi)002:788: don de gsang sngags nyid kyis bkrol //
NK038(nyi)002:789: le'u gsum pa nyid du shes /
NK038(nyi)002:790: nyams dga' phun su tshogs pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:791: gnas mchog dam pa yid 'ong bar //
NK038(nyi)002:792: tshul dang mthun pa'i rdzas kun bsog /
NK038(nyi)002:793: man+dala la sogs mdzes byas la //
NK038(nyi)002:794: khrus bya mchod pa'i rdzas kun bsog /
NK038(nyi)002:795: ngang las lha bsgoms snying gar h'u //
NK038(nyi)002:796: bgegs bskrad phyogs bsrung ra ba gur //
NK038(nyi)002:797: la drung 'od zer dbang po dgug /
NK038(nyi)002:799: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra he ru ka badz+ra
NK038(nyi)002:800: kro d+ha ra dza ma h+aa dz+ny+aa na man+da la
NK038(nyi)002:801: h'u / yon chab bdug spos mar me dri //
NK038(nyi)002:802: me tog gtor ma bdud rtsi khrag /
NK038(nyi)002:803: dngos sam yid sprul sngags kyis dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:804: sdig pa bshags pa 'di yang brjod //
NK038(nyi)002:805: bdag 'dra log pa'i stobs bdag gis //
NK038(nyi)002:806: thog mtha' med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK038(nyi)002:808: skye ba mang por lus blangs pa //
NK038(nyi)002:809: sus kyang ma byas rang gi las //
NK038(nyi)002:810: de tsam cha gcig don spyad na //
NK038(nyi)002:811: da tsam don gyi sangs rgyas zin //
NK038(nyi)002:812: rang lus gtong ba ma phod cing //
NK038(nyi)002:813: chags pa'i mtha' la mngon zhen pas //
NK038(nyi)002:814: zug rngu nad kyis zin pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:815: srid pa'i btson rar chud pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)002:816: mkha' la mdud pa rgyab pas nyes //
NK038(nyi)002:818: las kyi rlung gi nyes par nges //
NK038(nyi)002:819: dus gsum rgyal pa ma lus la //
NK038(nyi)002:821: rdo rje sems dpa' yid tshim yid skyabs stobs //
NK038(nyi)002:822: rdo rje sems dpa' nye zhing brtan par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:823: bde bar gyur cig kun tu bde gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)002:824: shin tu bdag la thugs rje chags par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:825: bdag nyid shin tu bde bar 'gyur mdzad cing //
NK038(nyi)002:826: dngos grub thams cad bdag la myur du stsol //
NK038(nyi)002:827: 'phrin las thams cad bdag la dag par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:828: sems dpa' dpal du mdzod cig thugs rjes bde //
NK038(nyi)002:829: bcom ldan de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kun //
NK038(nyi)002:830: rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil du bdag dril cig /
NK038(nyi)002:831: rdo rje 'byung ba chen po'i dam tshig gi //
NK038(nyi)002:832: sems dpa' skye med klong du dag par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:833: de 'am yang na sdig bshags bya //
NK038(nyi)002:834: ta ke ma ta ke ma phata /
NK038(nyi)002:838: dang po stong nyid dag par bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:839: dang po 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim //
NK038(nyi)002:840: rang snang gnas dang lhar gsal mchod pa dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:841: badz+ra a mri ta sarba man+da la h'u h+r+aihth+aah ma h+aa ba lim ta te dz+wa b+ha ling+ta h'u /
NK038(nyi)002:842: ma h+aa rak+ta ra ga shu ne ta ma h+aa sur+ya man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)002:843: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK038(nyi)002:844: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK038(nyi)002:845: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK038(nyi)002:846: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK038(nyi)002:847: stong nyid rab tu gsal ba las //
NK038(nyi)002:848: snying rje'i yul du bsgom bya zhing //
NK038(nyi)002:849: dbyer med ye shes rang gsal ba'i //
NK038(nyi)002:850: yi ge h'u du bsgom par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:851: h'u e yam ram kim ram /
NK038(nyi)002:852: go 'byed ye shes bsdud pa'i rlung //
NK038(nyi)002:853: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)002:854: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrug pa'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)002:855: kem rus chen po'i ri rab kyi //
NK038(nyi)002:856: steng gi 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK038(nyi)002:857: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK038(nyi)002:861: ma h+aa sur+ya man+da la ti ra bam /
NK038(nyi)002:863: gru chad bzhi yi rnam par brgyan //
NK038(nyi)002:864: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)002:865: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK038(nyi)002:866: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi mas brjid //
NK038(nyi)002:868: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK038(nyi)002:869: gtum po dam gyi spar bas ni //
NK038(nyi)002:870: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK038(nyi)002:872: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:875: bud+d+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:876: bud+d+ha ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sh+tmo /
NK038(nyi)002:877: rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai ri he ru ka h'u phatah rat+na ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sh+tmo /
NK038(nyi)002:878: pad+ma sh+ri he ru ka h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:879: pad+ma ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sh+tmo /
NK038(nyi)002:880: karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)002:881: karma ma h+aa kro ti shwo ri sh+tmo /
NK038(nyi)002:892: badz+ra bya tri mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)002:893: badz+ra sri la mu ka he /
NK038(nyi)002:894: badz+ra shwa na mu ka he /
NK038(nyi)002:895: badz+ra kri ta mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)002:896: badz+ra kam ka mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)002:897: badz+ra kha kha mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)002:898: badz+ra hu lu ka mu ka he /
NK038(nyi)002:899: phata badz+ra a r+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK038(nyi)002:902: badz+ra sa mi sa la ya ba to ho /
NK038(nyi)002:903: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:904: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:905: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:906: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:908: ma h+aa shu dz+nya na badz+ra a ra ri sha /
NK038(nyi)002:909: sa man+ta pra ta be sha /
NK038(nyi)002:910: tri ta a nu ta na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha at+ma ko&aham /
NK038(nyi)002:911: rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)002:912: rang gi snying gi 'od zer dang //
NK038(nyi)002:913: dbyangs dang ldan pa'i lha mo yis //
NK038(nyi)002:914: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK038(nyi)002:915: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK038(nyi)002:916: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drangs so //
NK038(nyi)002:917: rang snang dbye ba med par bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:919: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK038(nyi)002:920: bsnyen pa'i da la rab tu rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:921: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK038(nyi)002:922: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)002:923: e ha he a na ya hoh dzah h'u bam ho ram /
NK038(nyi)002:924: dmigs med mkha' ltar khyab pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)002:925: spyan drangs gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)002:926: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK038(nyi)002:927: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:928: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u ///
NK038(nyi)002:929: khro la khros pa zhi mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)002:930: thugs rje'i khro dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)002:931: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK038(nyi)002:932: de nyid du ni bdag la gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:933: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya phata //
NK038(nyi)002:934: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya sh+tmo //
NK038(nyi)002:935: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya ho /
NK038(nyi)002:936: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK038(nyi)002:937: byams dang snying rje dgrar 'dzin mi mnga' yang //
NK038(nyi)002:938: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK038(nyi)002:939: dpal chen yab yum sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)002:940: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK038(nyi)002:941: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK038(nyi)002:942: ma sring byams ma'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK038(nyi)002:943: gnas yul khro mo'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)002:944: 'jig rten 'khor los bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug ma //
NK038(nyi)002:945: ci bgyi bka' nyan yang sprul bsam mi khyab //
NK038(nyi)002:946: bdud 'dul ye shes pho nya mang po'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)002:947: 'khor bcas rab 'bar kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)002:948: a ti pu hoh pra ti pra ho ban d+ha na ro ya mi //
NK038(nyi)002:949: sh+ri ban yo ki ni ti ti ka ni hoh sku gsung thugs su bdag sbyor ba //
NK038(nyi)002:950: pho brang dkyil 'khor rang las sprul //
NK038(nyi)002:951: nga ni bdud kyi bdud stag ste //
NK038(nyi)002:952: thams cad ma lus dbang du bsdu //
NK038(nyi)002:953: sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba du sh+tam ma ra ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK038(nyi)002:954: snying gar mi spyod rdo rje mtshan //
NK038(nyi)002:955: h'u las lha mo brgyad spros te //
NK038(nyi)002:956: dbyangs dang ldan pas mchod par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:958: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK038(nyi)002:959: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK038(nyi)002:960: rtsa ba 'bum phrag yangs pa'i bcud //
NK038(nyi)002:961: sangs rgyas stong len gdam ngag sbyin pa chen po 'di sbyin bskul lo bstod do mchod do //
NK038(nyi)002:962: rtsa sngag kun gyis rim par dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:963: yig 'bru gsum gyis dngos grub blang //
NK038(nyi)002:964: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)002:965: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK038(nyi)002:966: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK038(nyi)002:967: dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:968: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra dang s+t+wam /
NK038(nyi)002:969: go'u na ro'u tri badz+ra kha ram yo gi ni /
NK038(nyi)002:971: pra ti dza ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)002:972: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po bdag /
NK038(nyi)002:973: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:974: dges mnyam mchog gi sbyin pa dbyings kyi ngang du thim //
NK038(nyi)002:975: zag med bdud rtsi'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)002:976: ma ha pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi //
NK038(nyi)002:977: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK038(nyi)002:978: dur khrod chen po gnas brgyad nas //
NK038(nyi)002:980: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK038(nyi)002:981: zhing chen gsar rnying sti rar bcas //
NK038(nyi)002:982: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK038(nyi)002:984: ma lus bzhes nas bsnams su gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:985: ma h+aa rak+ta kh+aa ram kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)002:987: dgyes snyams mchog gi mchod pas stim //
NK038(nyi)002:990: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK038(nyi)002:991: mi dmigs thugs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)002:992: thams cad ye shes rang snang ba //
NK038(nyi)002:993: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyi ngang //
NK038(nyi)002:994: ma mo rnams kyi bstod tshig dbul //
NK038(nyi)002:996: h+r+aih myos byed stong bas lhag par bde bar 'dod pa'i gzugs ston pa //
NK038(nyi)002:997: gdul bya'i dbang gis gshin rje stong bas lhag par rab tu 'jigs //
NK038(nyi)002:998: zhi ba'i skur yang tshangs pa stong bas lhag par rab tu ston //
NK038(nyi)002:999: thams cad dag par mos pas dkyil 'khor gsum du snang bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:1000: h+r+aih rnam par 'dul ba'i don mthong thabs kyis rnam par non //
NK038(nyi)002:1005: dbang phyug thams cad shig rab tu shig /
NK038(nyi)002:1006: rab kyi rtsal gyis stobs kyis ngo mthon dbang phyug non //
NK038(nyi)002:1007: h+r+aih rtsal chen ru lu'i mig gsum sa la gsum grus drongs //
NK038(nyi)002:1008: h+r+aih rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa'i stobs kyis ngo mthon mthu chen non //
NK038(nyi)002:1009: ru tra ma tra snying la dpal mos drongs shig rab drongs shig /
NK038(nyi)002:1010: rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa'i stobs kyis ngo mtshar tshangs pa non //
NK038(nyi)002:1011: sbyor chen tshangs pa sgrol ma drongs shig sma ra ta //
NK038(nyi)002:1012: h+r+aih rab kyi rtsal gyi non pa'i stobs kyis ngo mthong dga' dbang non /
NK038(nyi)002:1013: sbyor chen kun gyis bdag la dga' drongs a la la //
NK038(nyi)002:1014: h+r+aih rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthon ru tra non /
NK038(nyi)002:1015: sbyor chen kro ti shwa ri drongs shig rab drongs shig /
NK038(nyi)002:1016: snying rje gang la bya'am mi bya ba //
NK038(nyi)002:1017: yongs su rtog pa de dag med kyang sla //
NK038(nyi)002:1018: de 'dra'i snying rje sgyu ma yin pas na //
NK038(nyi)002:1019: de la rje zhes su zhig zer //
NK038(nyi)002:1020: gdul bya gang la bya'am mi bya ba //
NK038(nyi)002:1021: yongs su rtog pa de dag med kyang sla //
NK038(nyi)002:1022: de 'dra'i rtul ba sgyu ma yin pas na //
NK038(nyi)002:1023: de la rtul zhes su zhig zer //
NK038(nyi)002:1027: ko la ka la sh+ta khra /
NK038(nyi)002:1028: rtog pa'i rgyud kyi gdul bya ma lus rnams //
NK038(nyi)002:1029: ye shes ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par bstod //
NK038(nyi)002:1032: sa ma ya bag sha h'u /
NK038(nyi)002:1033: ru lu ru lu phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:1034: 'bar ba'i da la gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)002:1035: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pas dgyes par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:1036: dam tshig nyams chags 'gal 'khrul bshags par bgyi //
NK038(nyi)002:1037: thun mongs mchog gi dngos grub dus 'dir stsol //
NK038(nyi)002:1038: 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)002:1039: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)002:1040: rang gi phyag rgya'i nga rgyal la //
NK038(nyi)002:1041: sngon byung ba yi khro bo'am //
NK038(nyi)002:1042: spyan ras gzigs sam drag po'i gshed //
NK038(nyi)002:1043: srin po dbu dgu bco brgyad phyag /
NK038(nyi)002:1044: thugs kar drag po'i 'khor lo bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:1045: ru lu rtsa ba'i sngags la 'bum mam bye ba rdzogs par bya /
NK038(nyi)002:1046: ru lu phyi ltar bzlas pa ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1047: thugs ka'i h'u gi 'od zer las //
NK038(nyi)002:1048: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)002:1049: bcud kyi 'bar pa lnga bcu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:1050: kun kyang sngags kyi sgra sgrogs shing //
NK038(nyi)002:1051: phar 'phros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK038(nyi)002:1052: tshur 'dus pas ni dngos grub thob //
NK038(nyi)002:1054: ru lu gong ma khro mo brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:1055: 'og ma za byed phra men brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:1056: h'u ni khrag 'thung yab yum bcu //
NK038(nyi)002:1057: phata ni ye shes sgo ma bzhi //
NK038(nyi)002:1058: b+h+yo ni dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:1059: ru lu h'u gis mchod par bzhes //
NK038(nyi)002:1060: dam tshig da la byin gyis rlabs //
NK038(nyi)002:1061: sgrub pa po la dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)002:1062: bar chad dgra bgegs thugs rjes sgrol //
NK038(nyi)002:1063: ru lu bzlas lugs rnam dag ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1064: tsit+ta ye shes gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)002:1065: rig pa ye shes sems dpa' la //
NK038(nyi)002:1066: don gyi lha mo lnga yis bskor //
NK038(nyi)002:1067: nyid kyi h'u las 'bru brgyad mthing //
NK038(nyi)002:1069: yang na ljags kyi pad+mo la //
NK038(nyi)002:1070: gsung gi rdo rje zla tshes bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:1073: gsung thos dngos grub thob par bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:1074: yang na bde chen 'khor lo las //
NK038(nyi)002:1075: sku yi rdo rje zla ba bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:1077: lus kyi sgrib sbyangs brtan par bsdu //
NK038(nyi)002:1078: snang ba thams cad lha yi sku //
NK038(nyi)002:1079: grags pa thams cad sngags kyi sgra //
NK038(nyi)002:1080: dran rtogs thams cad ye shes lnga //
NK038(nyi)002:1081: dkar po 'phros pas bde ba che //
NK038(nyi)002:1082: dmar po 'phros pas kun la khyab //
NK038(nyi)002:1083: dkar dmar mtshams na he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)002:1084: mthing nag khro tshogs bsam yas kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1085: nam mkha' bar snang sa gzhi gang //
NK038(nyi)002:1086: kun kyang ru lu'i sgra sgrogs shing //
NK038(nyi)002:1088: mthing gar bsdus la dngos grub mchog /
NK038(nyi)002:1089: ru lu nang gi bzlas thabs ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1090: rang lus 'od kyi gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)002:1091: phung po lnga ni khrag 'thung lnga //
NK038(nyi)002:1092: 'byung ba lnga ni yum gyi sku //
NK038(nyi)002:1093: rnam shes tshogs brgyad khro mo brgyad //
NK038(nyi)002:1094: yul dang dbyer med phra men ma'o //
NK038(nyi)002:1095: lta ba'i bye brag sgo ma'o //
NK038(nyi)002:1096: da ba nyes pa'i nyon mongs dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1097: rtog dpyod dbang mo'i rang bzhin yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1098: ri rab til 'bru'i tshul bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)002:1100: ru lu gsang bas bzlas pa ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1102: byang chub sems kyi bzlas pa ste //
NK038(nyi)002:1104: yang na dbugs dang 'grogs la bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:1105: h'u gis phul nas phyir phyung nas //
NK038(nyi)002:1107: a la sems gtad gnas pa gsum //
NK038(nyi)002:1108: zhag gcig la ni dbugs kyi rgyun /
NK038(nyi)002:1109: nyi khri chig stong rgyu ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)002:1110: sngags ni nyi khri chig stong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1112: dpal chen khrag 'thung thugs kyi dpal be'u nas //
NK038(nyi)002:1113: ye shes sku mchog mtshon gang rin po che //
NK038(nyi)002:1114: zur brgyad steng na yi ge 'bru brgyad spro //
NK038(nyi)002:1115: bde chen byang chub sems kyi 'phro 'du 'di //
NK038(nyi)002:1116: rdo rje'i bzlas pa bsgrub chen nyid dang 'brel //
NK038(nyi)002:1117: ri rab ri'i rtse mo ru //
NK038(nyi)002:1118: dpal chen khrag 'thung rgyal ba yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1119: lha srin dbang bsdud dam la btags //
NK038(nyi)002:1120: gsang sngags ru lu 'bru brgyad ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1121: lha srin sde brgyad srog sngags yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1122: rngam zhing drag po'i nga ros bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:1123: sde brgyad dbang bsdu dam la 'dogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1124: bdag nyid chas su bzhugs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:1125: khro chen rngam pa'i nga rgyal gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1126: sde brgyad drag po'i sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)002:1127: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)002:1128: sarba sha trum ma ra ya rbad //
NK038(nyi)002:1129: ye shes lha bsgrub gdam pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)002:1130: gal po che yi dgongs pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1131: thun mtshams mnyam par bzhag pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1132: rang gi yid bzhin rin po che //
NK038(nyi)002:1133: yod par ma shes gtor bar dran //
NK038(nyi)002:1134: tshor bar 'dod na ji ltar bsam //
NK038(nyi)002:1135: sngon tshe nga yi gshen rje mchog /
NK038(nyi)002:1136: byams mgon dam pa zhig gis bstan //
NK038(nyi)002:1137: e ma'o khyod kyis mi shes sam //
NK038(nyi)002:1138: sgron mes mun khung gser 'tshol ltar //
NK038(nyi)002:1139: gsang ba'i snying po mdzod btol te //
NK038(nyi)002:1140: nges don khyod la bston par bya //
NK038(nyi)002:1141: thig le gcig gis kun la khyab //
NK038(nyi)002:1142: thams cad lung chen nges par bstan //
NK038(nyi)002:1143: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)002:1144: khrag 'thung lnga bcu brgyad du gsal //
NK038(nyi)002:1145: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lor rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1146: rang byung rang snang ye shes gsal //
NK038(nyi)002:1148: rtsol med ma bcos rnam par dag /
NK038(nyi)002:1149: thig le dwangs ma'i gdams pa ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1150: snying gi pad+ma dmar po la //
NK038(nyi)002:1151: thig le nyungs dkar tshad tsam bsgom //
NK038(nyi)002:1152: de las 'od zer rdul rnyed spro //
NK038(nyi)002:1153: mun sel dngos po kun sbyangs pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1154: thams cad ma bcos sku ru gsal //
NK038(nyi)002:1155: slar 'dus thig le'i ngang du thim //
NK038(nyi)002:1157: ma bcos gnyug ma'i ngang du gsal //
NK038(nyi)002:1158: rdzogs pa rlung la sems sbyang ba //
NK038(nyi)002:1159: rdo rje sems dpa' tsit+ta'i nang //
NK038(nyi)002:1161: dbus na rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1162: thig le 'od zer lnga dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)002:1163: de steng bde chen sa rlung ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1164: rnam par dag pa zla ba'i steng //
NK038(nyi)002:1166: nyi ma'i steng du chu rlung gnyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1167: rdo rje rin chen rin chen yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1168: snying ga'i 'od kyi g.yo rlung dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1169: sprul pa nyi ma'i me rlung gnyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1170: pad+ma rigs dang las rigs sogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1171: yam ldan dbus kyi thig le la //
NK038(nyi)002:1172: yam la yam du 'dris sam na //
NK038(nyi)002:1173: rig pa sems kyi rlung zin pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1175: yang na 'khor lo rnam pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)002:1176: bde chen sum cu rtsa gnyis ham /
NK038(nyi)002:1177: brtan pa'i yi ge thig le lam /
NK038(nyi)002:1178: longs spyod bcu drug lnga ldan //
NK038(nyi)002:1179: chu yi sa bon yi ge bam //
NK038(nyi)002:1180: snying gi brgyad dbus bzhi mdud h'u //
NK038(nyi)002:1181: brjod bral thig le yi ge mum //
NK038(nyi)002:1182: sprul pa drug tsu rtsa bzhi la //
NK038(nyi)002:1183: drod kyi cha 'dzin yi ge mam //
NK038(nyi)002:1185: rten la las rlung zin gyur nas //
NK038(nyi)002:1186: des kyang rig pa rang sa zin //
NK038(nyi)002:1187: yi ge yon tan stobs kyi 'grub //
NK038(nyi)002:1188: 'chi ka'i gsang lam sbyang ba ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1189: sa nyid chu la thim pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1190: kun mnyam zag pa med pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1191: lam gyi ye shes dang po skye //
NK038(nyi)002:1192: chu nyid me la thim pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1193: zag med ro brgya myong ba sdud //
NK038(nyi)002:1194: me nyid rlung la thim pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1195: 'gyu byed rang bzhin gsal snang nyid //
NK038(nyi)002:1196: glog gi rnam pa lta bu 'thung //
NK038(nyi)002:1197: rlung nyid rnam shes nam mkhar thim //
NK038(nyi)002:1198: rang gsal rig pa mar me 'dra //
NK038(nyi)002:1199: phyi nang mun pa rnam par sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)002:1200: nam mkha' lta bur mthong bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1201: phye bas rim par rtog pa char //
NK038(nyi)002:1202: bsgom pas snang zhugs phrad pa yin //
NK038(nyi)002:1203: mi rtag 'pho ba'i dus byung na /
NK038(nyi)002:1204: rig pa rlung nyid der bstan pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1206: rnam smin rigs la the tshom med //
NK038(nyi)002:1207: lam gyi ye shes 'char tshul ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1209: yid la byed pa'i ting 'dzin thob //
NK038(nyi)002:1210: sems gsum skye zhing mtha' bcu grol //
NK038(nyi)002:1211: rten pa bzhi pa sar gnas pa //
NK038(nyi)002:1214: sems gsum rdzogs te mtha' bcu shes //
NK038(nyi)002:1217: yongs su mi rtog ting 'dzin ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1218: smon lam lta bur chos lung ston //
NK038(nyi)002:1219: 'jig rten nor bu rin chen de //
NK038(nyi)002:1220: gang bar spyod pa'i ltas mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1221: sgyu ma spyod ba'i skyes bu de //
NK038(nyi)002:1222: 'khor du bsgyur ba'i cha byad du //
NK038(nyi)002:1223: rin chen bdun dang dpung tshogs kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1224: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ston //
NK038(nyi)002:1225: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1226: seng ge dag la zhon nas ni //
NK038(nyi)002:1227: thams cad gnon pa'i ltas mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1228: sgra brnyan dra bar lung ston 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1229: 'bras bu nyid la lam shes pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1230: lam gyi yan lag bde rdzogs dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1231: gzhan dag smin par bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)002:1232: ji ltar 'dod ltar thabs mchog sbyor //
NK038(nyi)002:1233: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1234: kun snang ting 'dzin nyid thob de //
NK038(nyi)002:1235: snang byed nyi zla 'khor lo bskor //
NK038(nyi)002:1236: thams cad gsal byed ltas mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1237: gdeng du gyur pa'i ngo bo yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1238: de nas rgyal tshab skyes bu de //
NK038(nyi)002:1239: chos kyi rgyal po gang de yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1240: gdung thob theg chen dga' ldan ston //
NK038(nyi)002:1241: mi gnas bcu dus cho 'phrul snang //
NK038(nyi)002:1242: sa bcu dag la gnas med kyang //
NK038(nyi)002:1243: gsang sngags don mchog ma red na //
NK038(nyi)002:1244: rnam pa thams cad thob mi 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1245: rnyed ma thag tu de rnyed 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1246: grol bar 'dod na bla ma bsten //
NK038(nyi)002:1247: rig pa rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK038(nyi)002:1248: byang chub sems kyi dal la rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1249: gsang sngags lam gyi rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)002:1250: rnal 'byor tshogs kyi logs spyod la //
NK038(nyi)002:1251: bsod nams tshogs kyi longs spyod rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1252: zhing khams rin chen yod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)002:1253: ston pa kun tu bzang po yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1254: sras mchog 'jam dpal chen po la //
NK038(nyi)002:1255: bshad pa bzhin du rtogs gyur na //
NK038(nyi)002:1256: gang la spyod kyang lam gyi grogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1257: dper na me la shing bsnan bzhin //
NK038(nyi)002:1258: mi 'gyur chos nyid rol pa yis //
NK038(nyi)002:1259: mdzad spyod gdeng dang ldan gyur na //
NK038(nyi)002:1260: rnam gsum tshul ni rol bar byed //
NK038(nyi)002:1261: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NK038(nyi)002:1262: 'byor pa'i yo byad rnam lnga ste //
NK038(nyi)002:1263: bza' btung bro gar gos brgyan dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1264: glu tshig tan gan rnam lnga'o //
NK038(nyi)002:1265: mdzad spyod gsum gyis nyams su blangs //
NK038(nyi)002:1266: skye shi med pa'i mdzad spyod dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1267: mi 'gyur rol pa'i mdzad spyod dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1269: mi 'gyur rol pa'i mdzad spyod dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1270: de la bye brag rnam gsum ste //
NK038(nyi)002:1271: gdos bcas don dang stun pa dang //
NK038(nyi)002:1272: dam rdzas blang dor med pa yi //
NK038(nyi)002:1273: mi gnas rol pa'i mdzad spyod do //
NK038(nyi)002:1274: spyod pa'i mtha' ni gsum yin te //
NK038(nyi)002:1275: rnam pa bzhi la rnam rol la //
NK038(nyi)002:1276: rang bzhin chos nyid rol pa'o //
NK038(nyi)002:1277: spyod pa'i yon tan rnams pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)002:1278: bza' dang btung ba'i longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1279: bde chen sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK038(nyi)002:1280: rgyan dang bgo ba'i longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1282: bro gar bskyod bskul longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1283: sa la 'jug dang stong la rgyug /
NK038(nyi)002:1284: glu tshig sgra yi longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1285: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)002:1286: ta na ga na'i longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1288: de bzhin 'byor ba'i longs spyod rnams //
NK038(nyi)002:1289: bgegs bskrad bdud rtsi gsang bar bya //
NK038(nyi)002:1290: sngags dang phyag rgya ting 'dzin gyis //
NK038(nyi)002:1291: rang snang 'dod yon drug tu snang //
NK038(nyi)002:1292: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la //
NK038(nyi)002:1293: ting 'dzin rdzas kyis rim bzhin mchod //
NK038(nyi)002:1294: brgyan mdzes gro gar glu dbyangs blang //
NK038(nyi)002:1295: tshogs la rol la ling ro bstim //
NK038(nyi)002:1296: bsgral la shes pa gnas chen spar //
NK038(nyi)002:1297: yab yum mkha' la sras su bskyed //
NK038(nyi)002:1298: h'u du shes nas gnyis med rol //
NK038(nyi)002:1299: dngos kyi bsod nams tshogs chen ldan //
NK038(nyi)002:1300: chos nyid shes na ye shes tshogs //
NK038(nyi)002:1301: bar skab lhag mas gnas bya bas //
NK038(nyi)002:1302: dam bsgrags mchod cing las la 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)002:1303: bsdu bsrung spyod lam kun kyang rdzogs so //
NK038(nyi)002:1304: de ltar bsgom zhing bsgrub byas na //
NK038(nyi)002:1306: mthar thug sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK038(nyi)002:1307: 'di ldeb bsod nams gang thob pa //
NK038(nyi)002:1308: phyi rim rnal 'byor don du bsngo //
NK038(nyi)002:1309: don rtags bar chad med sgrubs te //
NK038(nyi)002:1310: gong ma lta bu rdzogs par shog /
NK038(nyi)002:1311: yi dam lha sgrub cing dkyil 'khor 'dir bzhi'i don /
NK038(nyi)002:1312: slob dpon chen po rdo rje h'u mdzad kyi mdzad pa rdzogs so //
